BEGIN NOW THREE little Fairies sat in the fields eating their breakfast; END
BEGIN NOW each among the leaves of her favorite flower, Daisy, Primrose, END
BEGIN NOW and Violet, were happy as Elves need be. END
BEGIN NOW The morning wind gently rocked them to and fro, and the sun END
